        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Tax-preparer Enforcement, Accountability, and Minimum Standards Act or the TEAMS Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of the Treasury to regulate tax return preparers, including by sanctioning preparers for incompetence and disreputable behavior and by establishing minimum competency standards for preparers.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
